title: #92Noon! Vox in the Box! Dean Evason/Bill Guerin/Chad Greenway/Wes Walz
description: --Vox in the Box is back for the Friday Forechecking Feast. Dean Evason checks in to talk Wild Xs and Os, Bill Guerin talks Wild dollars and cents, Chad Greenway joins to give his draft night experience, and Wes Walz previews the Wild game tonight and an unfortunate edge catching from years past.
